name: Tourism Noosa
overview:
VisitNoosa.com.au was constructed on behalf of the official Tourism Noosa organization located in Tewantin, Queensland. The website was engineered in efforts to promote and support local community events and regional tourism within the Noosa region - with tourism being a major industry revenue stream in Queensland, Australia.

The current CEO is Steve Cooper, who employs a dedicated team of Tourism specialists on both a full time and part time basis. Both on and off-site marketing activities for visitnoosa.com.au are spear-headed by the industry liaison manager, Brad Harrison. The website has experienced significant growth in the past few years, with the Tourism Noosa brand name becoming renown for its online innovation in the Australian travel and tourism sector.

The focus of the Tourism Noosa is to connect users with the sights and surrounds of Noosa, Queensland by providing well-polished information on local events and attractions. Notable features of the website include the beach-cams, Noosa accommodation booking engine, events calendar and image galleries.
